{"error":0,"message":"","data":[{"show_ID":"1752","airdate":"1463940000","name_switch":"off","DJ":"Gazoo","showname":"PMPVsContinuousDevelopments","blurb":"Yes indeed. It's that time of the week. I've been toiling and slaving behind the curtains in order to bring you only the very best in last-moment effort.\n\nAstound, at how I wait until the very last seconds prior to the show, before coming up with compelling content.\n\nGasp, at how I look up basic facts which could easily been prepared in advance.\n\nAnd finally, shock at how I make light of it all, in a vain attempt to cover up my lack of professionalism.","nice_showname":"<strong><big>Gazoo<\/big><\/strong><br \/>PMPVsContinuousDevelopments","nice_airdate":"Sunday 22nd May, 2016<br \/>at 20:00 USRT"},{"show_ID":"1753","airdate":"1464544800","name_switch":"off","DJ":"Gazoo","showname":"PMPVsSanePlanningSensibleTomorrow","blurb":"What's this? Another show? Scheduled nearly a week in advance?\n\nAre you seeing things? Is this perhaps merely a database entry to make sure some piece of eletromatronic code works as intended?!\n\nIt is. But rejoice. A show will result regardless!","nice_showname":"<strong><big>Gazoo<\/big><\/strong><br \/>PMPVsSanePlanningSensibleTomorrow","nice_airdate":"Sunday 29th May, 2016<br \/>at 20:00 USRT"}]}